  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Magic Overflow is an arena shooter game where you combine spells to create your own magic. Craft a powerful magic, and defeat all enemies! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CRAFTING</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >magic crafting system like programming</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Connect spells</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181240/extras/7f170425dc638462c526778a9880dc45.avif?t=1739234299\" width=200 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And eliminate all the enemies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181240/extras/2fa87be5e5aa945425b8ec4b9c7b9911.poster.avif?t=1739234299\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181240/extras/2fa87be5e5aa945425b8ec4b9c7b9911.webm?t=1739234299\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181240/extras/2fa87be5e5aa945425b8ec4b9c7b9911.mp4?t=1739234299\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Spell Types</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are 6 types of spells</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181240/extras/35c56635760d09177ed8105ebe243e1c.avif?t=1739234299\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181240/extras_big/35c56635760d09177ed8105ebe243e1c.avif?t=1739234299 width=800 height=310 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Caster Spell - </strong>The start point of the magic</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Projectile Spell - </strong>Spawn a projectile</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Modifier Spell -</strong> Change the nature of the spell</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Event Spell - </strong>Cast the next spell whenever the projectile meets the requirements</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Action Spell - </strong>Let the projectile take some action</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Common Spell - </strong>Useful spell that help create magic</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >How many rounds can you survive?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181240/extras/779435583ce31f645bdde5545ab4d24c.poster.avif?t=1739234299\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181240/extras/779435583ce31f645bdde5545ab4d24c.webm?t=1739234299\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181240/extras/779435583ce31f645bdde5545ab4d24c.mp4?t=1739234299\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
